{"tid":856675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你有冇擔心個未來又會唔會去正視","createTime":"2018-10-10T16:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T17:14:34.000Z","uid":160537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"749ba4368f6044404c3d24105dbdbcb612921019","tid":856675,"uid":160537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"你有冇關心個世界依加發生緊嘅事<br />\n你有冇擔心個未來又會唔會去正視<br />\n究竟幾時開始 人變得冷漠自私<br />\n淨係知 點樣追求名利易D<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫療: 多蝗蟲排隊，影響港人服務，例如打針分孕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n教育：早喺幾年前已經有普教中，打壓廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n娛樂：康文署班被蝗蟲上網瘋傳 齊體<br />\n報班。演唱會有支那人炒飛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n生態：去沙灘、行山唔處理垃圾。去貝澳捉啲小生物 影響生態平衡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交通：同市民逼港鐵，又唔禮讓。例如唔讓乘客落車、超坐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日常用品：早幾年前，北區嘅奶粉長期冇貨。大陸黑心食品搞到香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n房屋：有錢嘅就炒樓，窮嘅就爭公屋。<br />\n<br />\n政治：成班人打壓咗我哋爭取民主嘅熱誠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上面只係部分例子<br />\n佢哋一步步咁影響緊我哋嘅日常生活<br />\n睇住香港畀人㩒住嚟屌<br />\n大家唔可以再扮冇事唔關心㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家可以做嘅嘢而且又容易做嘅就係<br />\n向身邊嘅家人同朋友講吓時事<br />\n因為真係有人會政治冷感或者好親共<br />\n畀佢哋知道支那蝗蟲如何影響緊我哋<br />\n遲啲有大型示威 就會有更加多人企岀嚟<br />\n到時我哋爭取嘅勝算就會大少少<br />\n希望喺有生之年見證港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a37c1904b38f741397d09af757d76ed029f4c8","tid":856675,"uid":160537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}